\ integer bitwise operators over the double representation (exact to 2^53)

\ ---- bit-and / bit-or / bit-xor ----
12 10 bit-and .
12 3 bit-or .
12 10 bit-xor .
0 255 bit-and .
255 0 bit-or .

\ ---- bit-not (two's-complement) ----
5 bit-not .
0 bit-not .
-1 bit-not .

\ ---- lshift ----
1 4 lshift .
3 2 lshift .
1 10 lshift .

\ ---- rshift (arithmetic) ----
13 1 rshift .
12 2 rshift .
1024 10 rshift .
-8 1 rshift .

\ ---- bit-packing: pack two bytes, then unpack ----
255 8 lshift 255 bit-or .
65535 8 rshift .
65535 8 rshift 255 bit-and .

\ ---- a 50-bit mask (meteor-style) round-trips exactly ----
1 49 lshift dup bit-or .

\ ---- lowest-bit (index of lowest set bit; -1 for 0) ----
1 lowest-bit .
8 lowest-bit .
12 lowest-bit .
1024 lowest-bit .
1 49 lshift lowest-bit .
0 lowest-bit .
